{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they couldn't have known.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They must've known something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But they couldn't have known the extent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't think they would have heard about Auschwitz, myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Again, I can't ask-- couldn't have asked my mother later, because she wouldn't have talked about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I don't think they would have known about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They certainly knew what's happening in Germany, obviously.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There are the terrible things there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I don't think that they-- they would have known about the extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Anyway, I'm-- I'm going off the-- going off the line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were, from then on, my father stopped us from even going near the window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "His idea was that, if you-- if you stay invisible, maybe we can.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he went-- he went along to my school and tried-- tried to-- to get the nuns to hide us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the nuns said, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father went to the bishop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were catacombs in my town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- Pecs is so old, there were catacombs everywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father asked the bishop to at least-- at least hide my young sister in the catacombs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, they wouldn't give any help, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, of course, there was no more school, need I say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The stars came in very, very quickly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't say exactly when, but, you know, if-- if it-- if it-- if I say a week, I don't think I'm much out-- straightaway.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People immediately started disappearing, because the dear Hungarians flooded the Gestapo with letters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember hearing that nowhere did they get the flood of letters as they got in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To-- to--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To give people to-- to put people in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, such and such is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Such and such is a Social-- Social Democrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
